<div id="UserCancellation" class="modal hide fade" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="myModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
  <div class="modal-header">
    <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-hidden="true">Ã—</button>
    <h3 id="myModalLabel">Are you sure ?</h3>
  </div>
  <div class="modal-body">
    <p>
      <h5>Your Profile, Boards and Masterpieces will be permanently deleted</h5>

      People who subscribed to your Pins or Boards will no longer be able to access your content. Links to your
      Pins will be redirected to a 404 Page. All your Content will permanently deleted.

      <h5>Your Account will be permanently deleted</h5>

      Once Cancellation is done, you can not reopen your Account. Your username will be set free.

    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="modal-footer">
    <button class="btn" data-dismiss="modal" aria-hidden="true">Close</button>
    <%= link_to registration_path(resource_name),  :data => { :confirm => "Are you sure?" }, :method => :delete, class: "btn btn-danger" do %>
        <i class="icon-warning-sign"></i> Cancel my Account
    <% end %>
  </div>
</div>

